2026-05-14T18:26:58.4137667Z 12    <!--
2026-05-14T18:26:58.4138000Z 13        Required for reminders to pop as full-screen notifications over the
2026-05-14T18:26:58.4138302Z 14        lock screen when the user enables "Full-Screen Notifications" in
